<div>

  <h1 class="font-extrabold text-blue-700 no-underline dark:text-blue-500">Icarus Modding Information</h1>

  <section class="m-6">
    <h2 class="text-icarus-500">Icarus Modding Links</h2>
    <div class="m-8">
      <h3>The Icarus Modding Discord Server</h3>
      <p class="m-12">
        <%= link_to "Join our Discord", "https://discord.gg/linkarus-icarus-modding-936621749733302292", target: "_blank", class: "anchor-blue" %>
      </p>
      <p class="m-12">
        This is the unofficial modding Discord server for Icarus.
        It's a great place to get help with modding, ask questions, and meet other modders.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="m-8">
      <h3>The Icarus Modding Upvote Page</h3>
      <p class="m-12">
        <%= link_to "Modding Upvote Page", "https://feedback.projectdaedalus.app/", target: "_blank", class: "anchor-blue" %>
      </p>
      <p class="m-12">
        This is a page where you can upvote or add new mods you'd like to see for Icarus.
        It's a great way to let us know what you want to see in the future.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="m-6">
    <h2 class="text-icarus-500">Icarus Modding Tools</h2>
    <div class="m-8">
      <h3>Icarus Mod Manager (aka IMM)</h3>
      <p class="m-12">
        This is a tool to help you manage your mods.
        It will allow you to install, uninstall, and update mods, including the ability to merge multiple mods.
        It will also allow you to create and manage your own mods.
      </p>
      <p class="m-12">
        More info, including download links, can be found on the projects <%= link_to "Github page", "https://github.com/Jimk72/Icarus_Software", class: "anchor-blue" %>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

</div>
